N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 ยง 133.4 - Cancellation

State Regulations

The Secretary of State shall cancel from the
register: (a) any certificate
concerning which the Secretary of State shall receive a voluntary request for
cancellation thereof from the person filing or from the assignee; and
(b) any certificate in respect of which a
court of competent jurisdiction shall order cancellation on any legal or
equitable ground. Notes
